Revert "ARROW-13440: Added a basic mapping generator that does not queue incoming jobs.  This allows it to forward async-reentrant pressure to the source.  Fixed some issues in the CSV reader that were preventing it from running truly parallel.  Performance is now significantly better but still not quite the same as the threaded reader.  For the NY taxi dataset the streaming read time went from ~7 seconds to ~1.6 seconds.  However, the file reader is still at ~0.8 seconds.  I\'ll do more investigation later."

ARROW-13440: Added a basic mapping generator that does not queue incoming jobs.  This allows it to forward async-reentrant pressure to the source.  Fixed some issues in the CSV reader that were preventing it from running truly parallel.  Performance is now significantly better but still not quite the same as the threaded reader.  For the NY taxi dataset the streaming read time went from ~7 seconds to ~1.6 seconds.  However, the file reader is still at ~0.8 seconds.  I\'ll do more investigation later.
